{"filter":false,"title":"IBM-innovation-summit.php","tooltip":"/digitalsummit/schedule/IBM-innovation-summit.php","undoManager":{"mark":52,"position":52,"stack":[[{"start":{"row":306,"column":20},"end":{"row":306,"column":538},"action":"remove","lines":["Miracle and IBM bring to you a full day of innovation, learning and live demos with multiple reputed speakers. The summit will cover various IBM technologies including IBM Bluemix, Watson and Node JS. The core part of the summit will focus on how you can use a cloud platform like IBM Bluemix to build next-gen applications around Cognitive and the Internet of Things. Come and join us on December 15th as we take you through the next wave of technology and how you can build innovative and life-changing applications."],"id":2}],[{"start":{"row":306,"column":20},"end":{"row":306,"column":380},"action":"insert","lines":["Miracle and IBM brought you a full day of innovation, learning and live demos with multiple reputed speakers. The summit covered various IBM technologies including IBM Bluemix, Watson and Node JS. The core part of the summit was focused on how to use a cloud platform like IBM Bluemix to build next-gen applications around Cognitive and the Internet of Things."],"id":3}],[{"start":{"row":311,"column":8},"end":{"row":317,"column":18},"action":"remove","lines":["<div class=\"row\">","            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">","            ","               <center><a href=\"../registration.php\" ><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-info col-sm-12\">Register for the Summit today!</button></a></center>","            </div>","            ","            </div>"],"id":4}],[{"start":{"row":377,"column":47},"end":{"row":377,"column":743},"action":"remove","lines":["<strong>Internet of Things (IoT)</strong> refers to an emerging paradigm that seamlessly integrates a large number of smart objects over Internet. These smart objects have the ability to sense the environment, communicate with each other and interpret the data, to make sound judgements, respond to events and irregularities promptly, without any human intervention. <strong>It’s not “the future,” it’s now - this year, next year and year after.</strong> These set of connected devices are predicted to cross over 30 Billion mark by the year 2020, as per the reports published by top Research & Advisory experts.<strong> IoT’s true value lies in the data, the interconnected items share.</strong>"],"id":6}],[{"start":{"row":377,"column":47},"end":{"row":377,"column":692},"action":"insert","lines":["Internet of Things (IoT) refers to an emerging paradigm that seamlessly integrates a large number of smart objects over Internet. These smart objects have the ability to sense the environment, communicate with each other and interpret the data, to make sound judgements, respond to events and irregularities promptly, without any human intervention. It’s not “the future,” it’s now - this year, next year and year after. These set of connected devices are predicted to cross over 30 Billion mark by the year 2020, as per the reports published by top Research & Advisory experts. IoT’s true value lies in the data, the interconnected items share."],"id":8}],[{"start":{"row":378,"column":47},"end":{"row":378,"column":203},"action":"remove","lines":["Here is where the industry’s most trusted IoT Platform, that provides industry leading analytics (predictive & cognitive) with unmatched scope & scalability"],"id":9}],[{"start":{"row":378,"column":47},"end":{"row":378,"column":203},"action":"insert","lines":["Here is where the industry’s most trusted IoT Platform, that provides industry leading analytics (predictive & cognitive) with unmatched scope & scalability"],"id":10}],[{"start":{"row":378,"column":592},"end":{"row":378,"column":994},"action":"remove","lines":["becomes the need of the hour, as we work towards handling billions of readings from millions of devices and make sense out of them by performing real time analytics, in a highly secured environment. Join us at Digital Summit 2016 in Vizag, as we brief you and discuss further on the role played by IBM Watson IoT Platform in creating an end to end IoT Solution and experience couple of hands-on demos, "],"id":11}],[{"start":{"row":378,"column":592},"end":{"row":378,"column":961},"action":"insert","lines":["becomes the need of the hour, as we work towards handling billions of readings from millions of devices and make sense out of them by performing real time analytics, in a highly secured environment. The experts at Digital Summit 2016 discussed on the role played by IBM Watson IoT Platform in creating an end to end IoT Solution and experience couple of hands-on demos,"],"id":12}],[{"start":{"row":381,"column":34},"end":{"row":381,"column":74},"action":"remove","lines":["Connect SensorTag to Watson IoT Platform"],"id":13}],[{"start":{"row":381,"column":34},"end":{"row":381,"column":74},"action":"insert","lines":["Connect SensorTag to Watson IoT Platform"],"id":14}],[{"start":{"row":382,"column":34},"end":{"row":382,"column":77},"action":"remove","lines":["Chatbot that works as your Office Concierge"],"id":15}],[{"start":{"row":382,"column":34},"end":{"row":382,"column":77},"action":"insert","lines":["Chatbot that works as your Office Concierge"],"id":16}],[{"start":{"row":383,"column":34},"end":{"row":383,"column":62},"action":"remove","lines":["Cognitive Elevator Assistant"],"id":17}],[{"start":{"row":383,"column":34},"end":{"row":383,"column":62},"action":"insert","lines":["Cognitive Elevator Assistant"],"id":18}],[{"start":{"row":384,"column":34},"end":{"row":384,"column":72},"action":"remove","lines":["Real Time Analytics on Elevator Events"],"id":19}],[{"start":{"row":384,"column":34},"end":{"row":384,"column":72},"action":"insert","lines":["Real Time Analytics on Elevator Events"],"id":20}],[{"start":{"row":481,"column":28},"end":{"row":481,"column":576},"action":"remove","lines":["The days of terminator are not are not far away, and as we